Get to know the No. 48 driver better before he climbs behind the wheel of the @allyracing Chevy @daytona!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 05, 2021 tagging @axaltaracing. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
@wgi1948, we're ready for you. 😎 

#HendrickNation, hands up if you can't wait for Sunday's action! 🙌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 05, 2021 tagging @jeffgordonweb. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text:
Today's #TBT looks back on @jeffgordonweb's final win @wgi1948! 

His 2001 victory marked his fourth at the road course after capturing the checkered flag. 🏁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hendrick Motorsports on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'HAPPY BIRTHDAY FINAL TIME ALAN GUSTAFSON CHAD KNAUS Handrick Hendrj'.

node.text: A big happy birthday to @napaknowhow crew chief Alan Gustafson and our VP of competition, Chad Knaus!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 04, 2021 tagging @napaknowhow. May be an image of car, road and text that says 'WATKINS GLEN INTERNATIONAL SUNDAY, AUGUST 8 3 PM ET| «BNBCSN ELLIOTT KED'.

node.text:
Win six of the last eight road course races: ✔️ 

Tune in Sunday to catch @chaseelliott9 in the @napaknowhow Chevy @wgi1948!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 04, 2021 tagging @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
The starting lineup has been set for @wgi1948!

@kylelarsonracin will take the green flag from fourth, followed by @alex_bowman in 10th, @chaseelliott9 in 11th and @williambyron in 15th.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 04, 2021 tagging @jeffgordonweb. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'BIRTHDAY HAPPY BIRTHDAY JEFF GORDON'.

node.text: Today we celebrate @jeffgordonweb as we wish him a very happy birthday!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 03, 2021 tagging @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of car, road and text that says 'LARSON ไa S WATKINS GLEN INTERNATIONAL SUNDAY, AUGUST 3 PM ,83 ET MNBCS'.

node.text: Leading 61 laps on road courses so far this year, tune in Sunday as @kylelarsonracin looks to lay down more fast laps @wgi1948! 🙌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 02, 2021 tagging @axaltaracing. May be an image of car.

node.text:
Our #MondayMotivation? It's race week. 🙌 

Who else is ready to see our Chevys back on track @wgi1948?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 01, 2021 tagging @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
All smiles because just one week until racing returns!

Comment below with a 😀 if you are just as excited as we are to kick off the high-speed action next Sunday @wgi1948.
